The Art Interest Questionnaire draws

aiq_draws.Rd

Posterior draws for a multilevel Bayesian ordered logit model for the The Art Interest Questionnaire data from the "Art has the power to stretch the boundaries of moral behaviour" manuscript. Each raw correspond to a single sample from the posterior distribution. The model was compiled and sampled using cmdstanr library. The columns documentation is clearly excessive, but is written in an explicit form to confirm to CRAN requirements of documenting every single column.
